thread.title: TV | Supernatural

author: Fiona Flynn
title: TV | Supernatural
text: This fantasy drama is now going into its eleventh series would you believe and show no signs of letting up. Things aren't going too well for the brothers though as Dean is a demon and is running amok with Crowley, while Sam is left trying to figure out what the hell happened to him. Sigh. This is like Buffy and Angel ALL over again.
